<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to Shopora!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333">
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
      "
    >
      <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #4caf50">Welcome, <%= name %>!</h2>
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>
        We are excited to have you on board! Below are your account details:
      </p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
      <p>You can log in to your account by clicking the button below:</p>
      <p style="text-align: center">
        <a
          style="
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
          "
          >Log In</a
        >
      </p>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
